name: Skate Frog Vol.1
description:
This is the artwork from our compilation album.

We present a compilation album with one purpose; 
Giving new hope to disadvantaged child skaters through music.
This hope is in the form of a skateboard that will help make his dreams come true.

Why skateboarding?

Skateboarding is the most inclusive sport. Skateboarding does not look at differences in background, age, characteristics, abilities, status, conditions, ethnicity, culture, and others. Skateboarding can help build confidence and form long-term friendships.

100% from this NFT sales will be donated through Skate Fellas.

Kindly check Skate Fellas movement on their Instagram account @skatefellas.id
